{"tid":2141993,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"HKCC 社會科學(8C111)FM Q&A /TG Group","createTime":"2020-08-06T06:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T06:22:32.000Z","uid":305710,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7c6c48429d12e00cfe5d788cc5bd0697748eb522","tid":2141993,"uid":305710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:03:26.000Z","msg":"Q: 咩係8C111 <br />\nA: 應用社會科學學系<br />\nNS 係 Non Scheme<br />\nSC 係 Sociology &amp; Culture <br />\nPSY 係 Psychology <br />\nSPA 係 Social Policy &amp; Administration <br />\n<br />\n而8C123為 Higher Diploma in Social Work <br />\n<br />\nQ: 幾時先收到offer?<br />\nA: Email雖然寫1點起 但CC office 效率同政府有得比<br />\n所以你預3-4點先收到啦<br />\n<br />\nQ: HKCC 好唔好？易唔易升？<br />\nA: HKCC啲人話係Asso界一大 但我認為你只要個人努力 去邊到都可以升返上UGC <br />\n<br />\nQ: 讀邊個Program 好啲？<br />\nA: 勁人讀邊個都勁 <br />\n<br />\nQ: HKCC 有咩值得你入讀？<br />\nA: 廁所<br />\n<br />\nQ: 簡錯科點算？<br />\nA: 讀完sem1可以轉program 唔洗驚<br />\n<br />\nQ: 8C111 可以轉 社工？<br />\nA: 唔可以 只有社工轉社會科學 社會科學唔可以轉社工<br />\n<br />\nQ: Poly HD悔終生 HKCC更稱心<br />\nA: 不適用於HKCC HD Program <br />\n<br />\nQ:升上去GPA要幾多？<br />\nA: Yr2 升yr3 （穩陣版）<br />\nHKU:<br />\nBSS&gt;3.9<br />\n<br />\nCU:(有interview)<br />\nSoci&gt;3.7<br />\n政政&gt;3.7<br />\nAnthro&gt;3.5(一定要擺first choice)<br />\nCultural study&gt;3.6(一定要擺first choice)<br />\nPsy&gt;3.9?(唔肯定）<br />\nGender&gt;3.4<br />\nCHP&gt;3.3<br />\n<br />\nCity:<br />\nAIS&gt;3.4<br />\nPPP&gt;3.4<br />\nCRIM/SOCI&gt;3.4<br />\nPsy&gt;3.7<br />\nSW&gt;3.4/5開始有interview<br />\n<br />\nPoly:<br />\nSPA&gt;3.4<br />\nAging&gt;3.4<br />\nSW&gt;3.6有interview？（唔肯定）<br />\n<br />\nBU:<br />\nGIS/soci&gt;3.3<br />\n<br />\nGroup List:<br />\n<br />\nHKCC Social Science<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Dt4K1Bondk_uovJ5vWPk2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDt4K1Bondk_uovJ5vWPk2w&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2FzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=ab843647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Dt4K1Bondk_uovJ5vWPk2w</a><br />\n<br />\nHigher Diploma in Social Work <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Dt4K1BxkFXXr3a-_nPztnA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDt4K1BxkFXXr3a-_nPztnA&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2FzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=7c3d8037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Dt4K1BxkFXXr3a-_nPztnA</a>"},{"pid":"0eaab3b3482a5645da78356af24cce3470ad4142","tid":2141993,"uid":305710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:19:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb089f3d00a38f0590a1b7ed5b7094bc2c9982fd","tid":2141993,"uid":305710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c8daa9604728220cd28d347785874e9e983418","tid":2141993,"uid":2368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:21:30.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"72a1f22b814137ee9ee86f868051f1b2790ade51","tid":2141993,"uid":308558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e70542c210201514b1e1cb25ed1401defa90c5","tid":2141993,"uid":305710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:46:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"254661f59831b47c0cdacbd2ac4e0fdac90561d3","tid":2141993,"uid":342912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:53:21.000Z","msg":"<